description: Returns an array of  IPSetSummary objects in the response.

nested_items.name: NextMarker
nested_items.description: To list more IPSet objects, submit another ListIPSets request, and in the next request use the NextMarker response value as the NextMarker value.

nested_items.name: IPSetId
nested_items.description: The IPSetId for an  IPSet. You can use IPSetId in a  GetIPSet request to get detailed information about an  IPSet.

nested_items.name: Name
nested_items.description: A friendly name or description of the  IPSet. You can't change the name of an IPSet after you create it.
